      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/intesa-ceo-says-rival-unicredit-can-create-value-through-merger-with-commerzbank-2024-10-03/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[意大利 Mediobanca 银行行长周四表示，欧洲的跨境银行合作环境并不有利，并补充称，意大利联合信贷银行 (UniCredit) 对德国商业银行 (Commerzbank) 的潜在收购不符合跨境交易的条件。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/intesa-ceo-says-rival-unicredit-can-create-value-through-merger-with-commerzbank-2024-10-03/</guid>
